SUBSTITUTE FOR
HOUSE BILL NO. 5551
A bill to amend 2016 PA 407, entitled
"Skilled trades regulation act,"
by amending section 1107 (MCL 339.6107).
THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF MICHIGAN ENACT:
1 Sec. 1107. (1) A person shall not engage in or work at the
2 business of a plumbing contractor, master plumber, journey plumber,
3 or apprentice plumber unless that person is licensed or registered
4 under this article. Except as provided in subsections (2) and (3),
5 only a licensed master or journey plumber shall perform plumbing. A
6 licensed master plumber shall be is in charge and responsible for
7 proper installation and conformance with the state construction
8 code. Plumbing shall must not be performed unless the plumbing
9 contractor who is responsible has obtained a permit from the this
